data.description: Charming Washington Local home with all the extras giving it that "something special" appeal! A covered front porch welcomes you home and is a perfect spot to unwind. The attached garage features a workbench for DIY enthusiasts. Newly tiled breezeway leads to a backyard patio nestled in a fenced & landscaped yard. The eat-in kitchen features a pantry, SS Appliances & vinyl plank flooring. Both bedrooms have ceiling fans for comfort. Below, a full dry bsmt is ready for your finishing touches. This home is a cozy retreat w/ modern amenities. Roof new in 2023, glass block, appl and LVT in 2022.
